HEADWORD: Brachial
<hw>Brach"i*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr> or <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>brachialis</ets> (<ets>bracch</ets>-), from
<ets>bracchium</ets> (<ets>bracch</ets>-) arm: cf. F.
<ets>brachial</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
